---
title: Turkey and Parmesan Patties with Sweet Potato Wedges and Broccoli
description: This delicious classic is packed with comforting, familiar flavours the whole family will love! Savoury turkey patties are paired with sweet potato wedges and tender broccoli, all covered in a fragrant rosemary-onion gravy to create one tasty dinner!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/galettes-de-dinde-au-parmesan-b7a37ebf.jpg
